nd spend them at the Upgrade Shop anytime. Want more? Crank up the challenge with <strong>fully adjustable difficulty settings. </strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/701b7e1c5d599371da0c83274f235b31.poster.avif?t=1659127933\" width=592 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/701b7e1c5d599371da0c83274f235b31.webm?t=1659127933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Earn score through completing <strong>unique mechanic objectives</strong>, from destroying stolen data to collecting holy blessings. These are hand-crafted and integrated to create a <strong>symphony of destruction and challenge.</strong>",
